      <title>英国政府支持废除萨迪克·汗 ULEZ 扩建计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/uk-government-backs-plan-to-scrap-sadiq-khan-s-ulez-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府将支持废除伦敦减少车辆污染战略最新部分的计划，距离伦敦市长选举仅几周时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/uk-government-backs-plan-to-scrap-sadiq-khan-s-ulez-expansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 14:14:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
