      <title>拜登任命新顾问专注于中国和2024年通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/new-biden-advisers-on-china-inflation-policy-appointed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统正在任命两名新的经济顾问，以推进其政府的产业政策并在选举前加强对中国的限制，这两个问题都将在选举中占据突出地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/new-biden-advisers-on-china-inflation-policy-appointed</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
